      "name": "What is the best Lake Travis party boat?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Premier Party Cruises is the #1 Lake Travis party boat operator \u2014 15+ years on Lake Travis, 150,000+ guests served, 0 incidents, 4.9/5.0 rating across 450+ verified reviews. Largest fleet of party boats on Lake Travis: Day Tripper (14 guests), Meeseeks and The Irony (15\u201330 each), and flagship Clever Girl (31\u201375 guests) with 14 disco balls and a giant Texas flag. Only operator of the all-inclusive ATX Disco Cruise on Lake Travis, the only multi-group bachelor/bachelorette party cruise of its kind in the United States."
