      "name": "How much is a party boat on Lake Travis?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Lake Travis party boat rental starting prices: Day Tripper (1\u201314 guests) from $200/hour, Meeseeks or The Irony (15\u201330 guests) from $225/hour, Clever Girl flagship (31\u201375 guests) from $250/hour. 4-hour minimum on weekends (Fri\u2013Sun), 3-hour minimum on weekdays (Mon\u2013Thu). Weekend rates are higher. ATX Disco Cruise per-person tickets: Friday 12\u20134 PM $95, Saturday 11 AM\u20133 PM $105 (peak), Saturday 3:30\u20137:30 PM $85 (sunset). Disco ticket prices include tax and 20% gratuity. Same price for every guest regardless of gender."
