      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Anderson Mill Marina, 13993 FM 2769, Leander, TX 78641 \u2014 the closest purpose-built party-boat marina to downtown Austin, approximately 25 minutes away via 183 North. Parking is FREE, plentiful, and right next to the dock. There are NO stairs to walk down to reach the boat. Uber/Lyft from downtown runs $35\u2013$55. Easy access from Austin, Round Rock, Cedar Park, Leander, and Lakeway."
