    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Are party boats on Lake Travis available year-round?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Private Lake Travis party boat charters operate year-round, every day, 12 months a year. Central Texas has mild winters so cruising stays comfortable most days. Off-peak months (November through February) offer better availability, easier booking, and a more exclusive lake experience. The seasonal window (March 1 \u2013 October 31) applies only to the shared public ATX Disco Cruise, not to private charters."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Can we bring alcohol on a Lake Travis party boat?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes \u2014 every Lake Travis party boat charter and every ATX Disco Cruise ticket is BYOB. Bring your own beer, wine, seltzers, and spirits in cans or plastic containers only (no glass on any Lake Travis vessel). Large coolers are included on every boat. Our sister company Party On Delivery delivers your BYOB order straight to the boat with everything iced down and ready before you board \u2014 retail prices, 100% buyback on unopened bottles. Alcohol is 21+ with valid ID; no underage drinking ever."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What's included with a Lake Travis party boat rental?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Every private Lake Travis party boat rental includes: licensed, experienced captain and professional crew, premium marine-grade Bluetooth audio system, large coolers (BYOB), sun + shade seating, climate-controlled restroom, full use of the boat for your group only, and customizable route on Lake Travis (Devil's Cove, Starnes Island, Hippie Hollow, or your own plan). Add the Essentials Package (+$100\u2013$200/hour depending on boat) for ice-stocked coolers + water dispenser + cups + 6-ft food table + vendor coordination. Add the Ultimate Package (+$250\u2013$350/hour) for giant lily pad + honor float + disco cups + bubble guns + champagne flutes + SPF-50 + full party setup."
