    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What's the difference between a Lake Travis party boat rental and the ATX Disco Cruise?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Lake Travis private party boat rental = exclusive whole-boat charter, year-round, any event type, you set the music and route, starting $200/hour. ATX Disco Cruise = shared multi-group party cruise on the Clever Girl flagship, per-person ticket, all-inclusive with DJ + photographer + floats included, March\u2013October only, bachelor and bachelorette groups only, three fixed time slots (Fri 12\u20134, Sat 11\u20133, Sat 3:30\u20137:30). Most corporate groups, weddings, birthdays, and families book a private charter; most bach groups book the Disco Cruise."
